  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "It was never meant to be both of you. One burns, one flows \u2014 but
    only one belongs here. I\u2019ve watched you move together, balance each other,
    survive where you shouldn\u2019t. But she feels it too, doesn\u2019t she? The
    pull beneath her feet. The way it calls her back. This place doesn\u2019t want
    balance. It wants her."
